36
00:02:00,647 --> 00:02:02,950
Yes, yes, absolutely. 9:30.

37
00:02:52,163 --> 00:02:56,459
Bagel for Marie, pancakes for Ariel, cereal for Bridgett.

38
00:02:56,526 --> 00:02:59,228
