61
00:04:01,265 --> 00:04:02,957
Huh? Oh, nobody.

62
00:04:03,695 --> 00:04:08,344
Nobody? Joe, I saw you talking on the phone to nobody at 7:15 this morning.

63
00:04:08,411 --> 00:04:10,643
